title: Sidewall, ca. 1900–40
creditline: Gift of Mark Bitter, Robert Bitter, Ward Bitter, and Tami Bitter Cook
description: Floral stripe. A circular red flower alternates with a green leaf. Each motif is outlined in brown and a brown stripe runs along either edge. There is also a double stripe in between the floral stripes. Printed on brown oatmeal paper.
